This folder contains slides, lecture notes, exercise and solutions for Andy Aschwanden's lecture on dynamics and thermodynamics of glaciers at McCarthy summer school on glaciology, June 2012.

Notes
-----

slides-handout target requires "pdfnup", from http://www2.warwick.ac.uk/fac/sci/statistics/staff/academic/firth/software/pdfjam/ (available through macports or apt-get, for example) 



